---
import Reveal from '../Reveal.astro';
---

<section class="px-gutter py-section mx-auto max-w-6xl" aria-label="Approach">
	<Reveal>
		<p class="font-display max-w-3xl text-3xl text-neutral-900 sm:text-4xl">
			Most business websites are technically capable of being great, but built without the
			discipline it takes to get there.
		</p>
	</Reveal>

	<Reveal class="delay-150">
		<p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl font-sans text-base text-neutral-600">
			Bloated frameworks. Unoptimized images. Generic templates dressed up as design systems. Sub-1s
			load times are the default, not an upgrade. Every decision starts from the same question: does
			this make the page faster, clearer, or easier to find?
		</p>
	</Reveal>
</section>
